revision.text: Note: The numbers for Wacan are varried since Wacans increases the growth rate of nearby berries. The XP per minute rate will be {{ #expr: 60/((30*60)/1.25)*1round2 }} for a single Wacan. However, if you plant a Wacan next to 8 ripe Wacans, that middle Wacan will have an XP per minute of {{ #expr: 60/((30*60)/(1.3^8*1.25))*1round2 }}. Each Wacan will have an XP per minute somewhere between these two values (with a level 0 Sprayduck equipped, and no boost mulch applied).
